Command                      Description                                      Example
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
open filename                Open a file or directory with the default app.   open file.txt
open -a "Application" file   Open a file with a specified application.        open -a "TextEdit" file.txt
open .                       Open the current directory in Finder.             open .
open -R filename             Reveal a file in Finder.                         open -R file.txt
open -e filename             Open a file in TextEdit.                        open -e file.txt
